{"tid":1847691,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[緊急] 再唔做呢2樣野，聽日為求封關既三罷行動注定人單勢孤","createTime":"2020-01-28T07:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T20:15:50.000Z","uid":258706,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c21a0209342ab7be466670e832fde9d0cc31cd95","tid":1847691,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"其實好多人都唔知聽日初五有三罷行動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  初五三罷既消息多數<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">只停留左係連登同TG</span> <br />\n好多冇用呢2個App既人根本唔知初五有三罷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  亦唔知今次三罷既意義<br />\n再唔做以下呢2樣野，聽日三罷行動注定人單勢孤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 街頭宣傳</span><br />\n仲記唔記得8.5點解咁多人出黎罷工？其中一個原因係<span style=\"color: gold;\">有充足既街頭宣傳</span>，eg 派傳單、貼罷工資訊上連儂牆、Airdrop...令到冇連登既淺黃、未退休既銀髮族都知當日有罷工同參與<br />\n要令到冇用呢2個App既人參與罷工，一定要有<span style=\"color: gold;\">足夠既街頭宣傳</span><br />\n而今次三罷涉及衛生同個人健康問題，相信已令到埋部份<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲都開始擔心</span> 唔封關會影響自身安危，宣傳品可能有機會打動佢地參與<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">特別建議：將初五三罷既消息貼上連儂牆，除左行動海報，<span style=\"color: pink;\">建議貼埋行動既意義同目的做解說</span>，打動淺藍一齊參與。<span style=\"color: pink;\">初四好多印刷舖仲未開</span>，有printer既朋友麻煩多多幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。另外，因衛生問題，唔鼓勵派傳單，可改為Airdrop。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 網上表態</span><br />\n有一班人知道聽日有三罷行動但唔夠膽罷工<br />\n但如果大家都係 IG / FB表態會罷，相信會令到仲猶疑緊罷唔罷既人一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時就有更多人參與，成功逼令政府封關既機會大增<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">距離初五得返唔夠9個鐘，距離大部份人今晚去完街開始返屋企仲有3、4個鐘!<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">請各社區有Printer既人準備print文宣+貼去連儂牆，多你一張Poster多好多!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗疫</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc8fc575d9eb70b726274d69b4305e7aa631b729","tid":1847691,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:10:53.000Z","msg":"只有燒到埋身<br />\n啲人先會做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ae2a7927fdf2a594d23ee2f7e806da8c31fbd8","tid":1847691,"uid":104698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:14:48.000Z","msg":"觀塘呀！好需要街頭宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日我諗好多同路人都會焗住照番<br />\n佢地可能需要助攻<br />\n利申 我罷"},{"pid":"ad6e54547c60e081d445efc230ef08c4caaf552d","tid":1847691,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:16:39.000Z","msg":"airdrop好"},{"pid":"cd34d0d1a2393b2c8cda5d4702fc06449964f898","tid":1847691,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60ae2a7927fdf2a594d23ee2f7e806da8c31fbd8","tid":1847691,"uid":104698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:14:48.000Z","msg":"觀塘呀！好需要街頭宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日我諗好多同路人都會焗住照番<br />\n佢地可能需要助攻<br />\n利申 我罷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"其他區都需要宣傳吖 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各區嘅朋友一起罷"},{"pid":"f21f192ce9410429436ad13398a952d7884cd330","tid":1847691,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653b87c286c6ccb00b17b8aba5b64fdd507e4bf0","tid":1847691,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8cdbc20ea8737d7cab2a45bc86cdfedb807dcf","tid":1847691,"uid":104698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:26:03.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"70b8752e40be284c841b664d345a4f3d069a7155","tid":1847691,"uid":82856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16fdb7200bd0acd6e236cac8299551cc278d287a","tid":1847691,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7a6eddf27af96047ef47496afccd4c1e6fdd5d","tid":1847691,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:45:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba21f12b3329daf725648d4dd300ebf113651965","tid":1847691,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea02374e3f32586f6178296bf65f421cd028d49","tid":1847691,"uid":317830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T20:15:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fa8a73aaadf462f5f12f3c8a6271f113b412cda4","tid":1847691,"uid":317830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T20:15:50.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}